      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Po\u017Car w\u015Br\u00F3d bestii",
        "Client": "Starszy Fugen",
        "Description": "Mam tu dla ciebie prawdziwe\r\nwyzwanie! Buahaha! Oho, jak\r\nstrzy\u017Ce uszami! Wiedzia\u0142em, \u017Ce\r\nci\u0119 to zainteresuje! Spu\u015B\u0107\r\nmanto tym bestiom, a dziadzio\r\nFugen da ci now\u0105 flori\u0119.\r\nPasuje? No to do roboty!",
        "Target": "Upoluj wszystkie cele",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Uma labareda entre feras",
        "Client": "Fugen, o anci\u00E3o",
        "Description": "Tenho um verdadeiro desafio aqui pra\r\nvoc\u00EA, \u003CLSNR {Guri} {Guria}\u003E! Buahaha! Olha s\u00F3 essas\r\norelhas em p\u00E9! Eu sabia que voc\u00EA se\r\ninteressaria! Derrota aquelas feras,\r\ne o velho Fugen aqui vai te dar um\r\nPetalar novo. Parece bom, n\u00E3o?\r\nAgora, manda brasa!",
        "Target": "Cace todos os monstros-alvos",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uB9F9\uB82C\uD55C \uBD88\uAF43\uACFC \uD65C\uBCF4\uD558\uB294 \uAC15\uC790",
        "Client": "\uCD0C\uC7A5 \uD6C4\uAC90",
